inspirational speech.

04:19.885 --> 04:22.906
Twattle and shy, I say.

04:22.987 --> 04:25.721
Then why am I here?

04:25.767 --> 04:29.560
You are here
to play your part.

04:33.986 --> 04:35.914
Credit mobilier.

04:35.991 --> 04:39.039
Credit mobilier
will be awarded

04:39.083 --> 04:42.998
