on the Union Pacific railroad.

04:43.000 --> 04:44.627
I own it.

04:44.712 --> 04:47.749
I'm giving you the chance
to get in on the ground floor.

04:49.177 --> 04:50.775
So, you'll be
paying yourself

04:51.011 --> 04:54.767
