this fresh air.

18:13.016 --> 18:14.261
Mmm.

18:14.314 --> 18:16.987
Mmm. Breathe deeply.

18:58.278 --> 19:02.525
So, uh, how many
slaves did you own?

19:04.350 --> 19:06.153
5 in all.

19:06.204 --> 19:08.360
I had me a small
tobacco farm.

19:08.407 --> 19:10.637
Any women?

19:10.639 --> 19:13.041
2.

19:13.130 --> 19:17.696
You ever, uh...
Sample the goods?

19:18.860 --> 19:23.234
Uh-uh.
It wasn't like that.

19:25.932 --> 19:27.374
Call.

19:28.723 --> 19:33.268
You, uh... bitter that
you had to give up your slaves?

19:34.939 --> 19:37.484
