year before the war started.

19:37.559 --> 19:39.490
Are you serious?

19:39.576 --> 19:42.349
I kept them on at wages.

19:42.422 --> 19:43.985
Ha ha.

19:44.052 --> 19:46.699
You are an odd duck,
Bohannon.

19:46.743 --> 19:49.088
I married a northerner.

19:49.161 --> 19:52.046
She convinced me
of the evils of slavery.

19:52.048 --> 19:57.348
So, you... you
released your slaves,

19:57.410 --> 19:59.166
yet you still
fought in the war.

19:59.301 --> 20:00.900
Why?

20:00.966 --> 20:03.593
Honor.

20:08.465 --> 20:12.259
The southerner
and his honor.

20:13.468 --> 20:15.755
Where is your wife now?

20:17.540 --> 20:20.109
She's dead.

20:23.487 --> 20:25.607
Did the war take her?

20:30.436 --> 20:32.935
Something like that.

20:48.636 --> 20:50.571
Think they heard us?

20:50.638 --> 20:53.503
Who cares?

20:53.563 --> 20:57.116
I don't want to torment
the poor bastards

20:57.245 --> 20:59.588
